│ 15026 /// Merges shuffle masks and emits final shuffle instruction, if required. It        │
│ 15027 /// supports shuffling of 2 input vectors. It implements lazy shuffles emission,     │
│ 15028 /// when the actual shuffle instruction is generated only if this is actually        │
│ 15029 /// required. Otherwise, the shuffle instruction emission is delayed till the        │
│ 15030 /// end of the process, to reduce the number of emitted instructions and further     │
│ 15031 /// analysis/transformations.                                                        │
│ 15032 /// The class also will look through the previously emitted shuffle instructions     │
│ 15033 /// and properly mark indices in mask as undef.                                      │
│ 15034 /// For example, given the code                                                      │
│ 15035 /// \code                                                                            │
│ 15036 /// %s1 = shufflevector <2 x ty> %0, poison, <1, 0>                                  │
│ 15037 /// %s2 = shufflevector <2 x ty> %1, poison, <1, 0>                                  │
│ 15038 /// \endcode                                                                         │
│ 15039 /// and if need to emit shuffle of %s1 and %s2 with mask <1, 0, 3, 2>, it will       │
│ 15040 /// look through %s1 and %s2 and emit                                                │
│ 15041 /// \code                                                                            │
│ 15042 /// %res = shufflevector <2 x ty> %0, %1, <0, 1, 2, 3>                               │
│ 15043 /// \endcode                                                                         │
│ 15044 /// instead.                                                                         │
│ 15045 /// If 2 operands are of different size, the smallest one will be resized and        │
│ 15046 /// the mask recalculated properly.                                                  │
│ 15047 /// For example, given the code                                                      │
│ 15048 /// \code                                                                            │
